content: Amazing. Best meditation app I've ever used. I've been using it for a few years now and it is just so good. Never found another one like it.
Love it. Hard to not giggle when he catches you with a funny phrase though.

I have used this app for years. It's fantastic here in 2020 as so much goes wrong. Helps me calm my mind when no other meditation can because of how much chaos is around me. I have recommended it to many. If you are reading this review, buy it!
Easy to use good app. Would love it if another update came through with more options or just another package to buy.

Love it! Ive used the video for relaxation for years but this is so much better. I do wish there was a pause button for the dialog so i could continue to listen to the "music" while allowing my breathing to find its own natural unhurried pace. Perhaps in a future update ;) Edited to add: im using a galaxy a51 and the app runs great. Smooth as silk.

15 Minute App - I rarely get to the end before falling asleep. I have had severe insomnia for decades, so this is a godsend. I knocked off one star because sometimes it spontaneously re-starts in the middle of the night.
Listen to this whilst doing my yoga stretchesüßò‚Äç‚ôÇÔ∏è Genuinely empowering and feel more positive after a session or 2... NamasteüòâüòÇ
Very honest. No BS. Also not for people without a sense of humour.
Just incredible.. Nothing works for me like this one does..
Wonderful to clear the mind when you are stressed or angry.
Found it on YouTube several years ago and recommend it to everybody!!!!!!! LOVE IT!!!!!!
Best money spent. Use this at least once a day!

The best way for me to get a little bit of meditation in each day. Was making me laugh a bit but I think I got that under control to better relax. I definitely want to get the book too and have let certain friends of mine who aren't into mindfulness meditation listen to it and they loved it as well. Thank you
I love this app.
I love this. It calms me down and makes me giggle. I would enjoy a 30 minute version also.

It's a great app overall. Use it before work, during work, as well as at home. Though while listening to it, wish I could loop it. It takes me a while to get into a deep meditation, but for a quickie this is the best. All thanks to YouTube for this over a year or two ago.

I absolutely love this! I find the brutal honesty of this meditation and how it just 'goes there' with its wording refreshingly cathartic and amusing. It's a great way to de-stress when you've had a bad day, especially ones full of those sh*theads that the meditation mentions(if you're dealing with them on a daily basis, you should probably do this meditation everyday). If you don't mind the salty language, I'd recommend this!
Ew
Best $2 I've ever spent. This is perfect for a quick break at work. It leaves me feeling happy and relaxed. Meditation mixed with laughter is wonderful!

I love the simplicity of the formatting for the app and links, though sometimes it freezes my phone (LG K-30, roughly an extra 30 seconds of processing) or doesn't link it and f*** if I know how that works. I use this app as often as I need to, and its a great spiritual tool for me. I dont think it is for everyone so I reccomend warning your favorite practitioners on the amount of wonderfully placed explatives since kids have a tendency to go "whats that" [boop] you: Welp... F it.
I've always made fun of meditation, but this app made it easy and funny. I work at a call center and this app has made getting through an 8 hour shift of hell calls so much easier and bearable.

The best $1.99 I've spent! Seriously, I am really glad I paid for this app. The meditations make me laugh and actually work for me. I've used it several times already and I downloaded it only a day ago. Pay for it, you won't regret it!
Love the app. Simple and relaxing. üòÄ
look, y'all will not regret paying for this app!!! this is the absolute best meditation app EVER
its my go to meditation app when i need it i love the meditations

Fast, simple, effective portal back to reality. This is an invaluable tool, and much more effective than most meditation apps I've used because I am not paralyzed with choices each time I launch the app. Just choose the time and start a funny, irreverent, yet 100% effective guided meditation!
This really is perfect!
Alchemic. ‚ô•Ô∏è
Finally a meditation app that doesn't take itself so seriously, once you go "Honest" you can't go back. Personal favorite!
THIS IS THE GREATEST MEDITATION APP EVAR. SRSLY.

The best $1.99 I've ever spent! It's meditation for "real" people and surprisingly is very relaxing. A must for ER nurses!
The only app I have ever rated on any app store because it truly deserves it
It's a little hard to take deep breaths while laughing, but the meditations work without them.

I love this app. But I believe that the issue is that it won't continue playing after my phone's screen goes to sleep. It used to continue without any problem. I will give it 5 stars after it gets fixed.
I love this app. I'm only giving it a one star because it has started crashing on me. Once the issue is fixed I will gladly change it.
As a techie I need to hear this daily. Turn it on in my office and then just enjoy....the breath in and then out.....
Best couple of bucks you'll ever spend.

Absolutely amazing relaxation app. Listen daily along with mindfulness

I'm not one to meditate.... However, I can effectively use this at least

Awesome

Fan-freaking-tasic. Sure to get you out of a funk on a bad day. Laughed until I cried

Funny, but it really can work as a meditative aid. i find itll get me to laugh and into a lighter mood

I tried to email the creator of the app because the times on the meditation do not last as long as they state. Specifically the five minute and the two minute. My email was kicked back to me. I paid for this app over a year ago and plan in 2018 to use it for my daily meditation practice. But the five minute one stops at random times usually around the three-minute mark and the two minute one last for maybe a minute. All I want is for the creator of the app to fix the problem!
Best

Best app!
This really works!! The language is right on par for me and it's really relaxing! This is the only app I've ever paid for!
Beautiful! Will there be a Windows phone version?
For sarcastic ppl like me this is AMAZING!!!! It speaks to my soul! If only he or someone would do yoga like this that would be great bc the namaste crap kills me!

Once you get over the surprise of tje comedic content, which never gets old, this really does work to calm you down. Listening to the short version was a team calming exercise on a really rough project I worked on last year.
This app is exactly what I need.  Love it!

This app is both hilarious and useful. Helped me a lot. One additional feature I would recommend is to include only the background music on loop too, so that I can learn to meditate without commentary
It's fun and it works if you work with it.
Best meditation app ever
Absolutely fantastic. I use this regularly to keep from exploding at the dumdums around me.
Seriously so good!! Made me snicker a lot the first few times, but it seriously helps disconnect and meditate!!
The best and most honest meditation app out there. A must for everyone who's serious about cleansing his soul from the BS of the surrounding world in the process of meditation.
Beautifully profane and profound. Pared down any pretence to bare reality. Breathe in peace.

The first app I am paying actual money for and it is absolutely worth it. I am not into meditation in general, but this app works perfectly for me. I have used it every day for a few days now, depending on how much time I feel like spending on it. But I don't think it is for everyone for sure.
Really helpful post 20 Jan 2017
I actually derive great joy and calm from listening to these "honest" meditations. After the initial belly laughs, I do use this app now for my daily mindfulness and relaxation.
Great. Thanks

Best meditation I've found. I listened to this at least weekly on YouTube, more now that I got the app. It's an extended version with more wonderful nuggets of stress relieving phrases delivered in a perfectly soothing voice. Love this so much. Truly does help me deal with the soul eating c*cksuckers in my life. So worth the $1.99. I want more!

I have used this app consistently for 2 weeks and I use it for my cleansing meditations. It's amazing how much I get out of his style!

I downloaded this because of the options of minutes to listen to. After listening to it for the first time, I figured what they meant by salty words. I like to listen to this because of my meditation help and also because my wife had a salty mouth before she died.
After paying to download the recordings, the first one cuts off several seconds before the end! What a rip-off: it's free to listen to it on YouTube.
It's funny but life does suck at times. This makes it so easy.

I've been listening and sharing this via youtube for the past year. I almost died the first time I heard it!!!  It's so dead on, it couldn't get anymore perfect. I was so excited when I found out there was an app. I listen to it everyday.
Yes.

I have tried meditation before but never can relax.  This actually works!  Absolutely amazing and absolutely honest reality!
It took a few listens to not laugh everytime a zinger flew out, but now it's relaxing and helps during those moments when I need to be reminded to breathe out the bullsh*t.

The meditation is hilarious, and I liked the app for about a half of a day... Then it started causing all my other apps to freeze up so that ONLY Netflix and Facebook could connect to my internet connection. Every other app and every other webpage couldn't connect anymore and were basically useless...I uninstalled this app and instantly everything else works properly again. Sadly it was a waste of $2 and left me disappointed.
Worth every penny (to me). I get why people b*tch about the price if it's for amusement only, but the original meditation changed my entire approach to meditating so I think it's worth it.
This app is probably valued at 1.96, but is definitely worth every bit of those extra three cents. Truly a great meditation!

I was a huge fan of the YouTube video I first saw this on. I loved it as a joke, but it legitimately is calming. I've been unsuccessful at many types of meditation, so having one that actually works for me (that is made to make me laugh at it) is gold. Love the different lengths of time to choose from, too. (I admittedly was doing the YouTube video on a loop, ha.) Well worth the $1.99.
First couple of times I couldn't stop giggling. What am I, 12? Yeesh. After that though, it's actually fun and relaxing.
I got it as a joke.  Joke on me, it actually a great app.  Really calming.
Did the 15 min in this app after trying the 2 min one that's on YouTube and it's even better. It's by far the best meditation I've ever done. Get this.
Best f***ing app to relax...

I was afraid this app would just loop the infamous YouTube video's audio but I took a chance and bought it. It's Not just a loop. It is a full 15 minute audio,  on down to 2 minutes,  with wonderful content. This is definitely the best 2 bucks I've spent.
Might be the best 1.99 I've ever spent xD
I f****** love this!
Awesomeness

Lighthearted cursing mixed with meditation is just what I need on a daily basis! With the added plus of picking the length to fit it in where you need it. In your car on break or in the bath after a long day. I love this. So glad someone had the brains to create it, and a version for Android too!
